OL,10,FOnce known as the place that runaway
OL,11,Flovers would elope to, Gretna Green is
OL,12,Fstill seen as one of the most romantic
OL,13,Fplaces to get married by many around
OL,14,Fthe world.
OL,16,FIt became the place for young couples
OL,17,Fto get married after the 1754 Marriage
OL,18,FAct was introduced in England and
OL,19,FWales.
