OL,6,FThe Law meant you couldn't marry
OL,7,Fwithout your parents' permission
OL,8,Funless you were over 21.
OL,10,FThe laws in Scotland were less strict,
OL,11,Fand so the little village on the
OL,12,FScottish border became world-famous as
OL,13,Fa place for young couples to rebel and
OL,14,Felope.
OL,16,FYou can still get married in many of
OL,17,Fits historic buildings including the
OL,18,FFamous Blacksmith Shop.
